{"tid":355842,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[補習笑話]英皇D名師咁吹得,個個都話7科5**狀元之師,咁合照呢?","createTime":"2017-08-11T15:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T14:21:12.000Z","uid":71314,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d102b94585fafc095dfc7086b025394728ad69e0","tid":355842,"uid":71314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  廖天恩仲話有4位狀元都補佢,但係俾人串極都拎唔出合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸俾hong sir幾萬條街,仲要扮晒女天皇咁,真係好撚嘔心chok撚晒樣好難頂,成個ar姑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洪偉權自從呃學生影相單野之後,又話自己7科5**狀元之師,屌你笑撚死人,今年洪偉權要借佢細佬班學生影相,自己實際上少人到仆街,呢張poster都係得20人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,佢拎到7科5**狀元合照真係乜都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20664031_1613426745336063_1005429778396639622_n.jpg?oh=0a8da6e659ca7b05955a952bcd6ee965&amp;oe=5A2C58A2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20664031_1613426745336063_1005429778396639622_n.jpg%3Foh%3D0a8da6e659ca7b05955a952bcd6ee965%26oe%3D5A2C58A2&h=7c23f3c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBen Fung仲吹到自己係咩5**比率最高(收到風佢影相連50 人都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ),自從偷片事件之後同洪偉權正式宣戰,但係自己又未夠料,少人到合照都唔敢post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 英皇呢間野特別多笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多正評再爆更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14be9c47e72411edcba74b92a1ac036f424cc11e","tid":355842,"ui